===World rankings points===
The Tour de France was one of 29&nbsp;events throughout the season that contributed points towards the [[2012 UCI World Tour]]. Points were awarded to the top 20&nbsp;finishers overall, and to the top five finishers in each stage.  Only riders on UCI ProTour teams were eligible to receive rankings points.<ref>{{cite web
|url=http://www.uci.ch/Modules/BUILTIN/getObject.asp?MenuId=MTU2MzU&ObjTypeCode=FILE&type=FILE&id=NDk5MDY&LangId=1
|title=Points scale <U+2013> UCI World Ranking|publisher=[[Union Cycliste Internationale]] |accessdate= 23 July 2012 }}</ref>

