===Prize money===
In total, around <U+20AC>3.5 million was distributed during the Tour. Initially, each team received <U+20AC>51,243, while each team with at least seven riders finishing the Tour received <U+20AC>1600 per rider. The winner of the General Classification received <U+20AC>450,000, with smaller prizes for each finishing position, down to <U+20AC>400 for the last rider.<ref name="Regulations">{{cite web |url=http://www.letour.fr/le-tour/2012/us/sporting-stakes-rules.html |title=Sporting stakes / rules |publisher=Le Tour |accessdate=23 July 2012 }}</ref>

