The stage winner was awarded <U+20AC>8,000 on a normal stage and <U+20AC>10,000 for a time trial. The money gradually decreases, with the 20th finisher receiving <U+20AC>200. The first person to cross the intermediate sprint wins <U+20AC>1,500. Money is also awarded for crossing the categorized climbs, for the best young rider of each stage, the most combative rider, and the best team of the stage.<ref name="Regulations" />

