Two other special prizes were awarded. The first to ascend the [[Col du Tourmalet]] and the [[Col de la Croix de Fer]] receive the souvenir [[Jacques Goddet]] and the souvenir [[Henri Desgrange]] respectively. Each prize awarded <U+20AC>5,000.<ref name="Regulations" />

